data.description: Welcome to the perfect blend of elegance, comfort, and modern living in this stunning Port Saint Lucie gem! This immaculate home offers a range of incredible features that you won't want to miss. Home Features: Plank Tile Flooring in the living area, Gourmet Kitchen: Create culinary masterpieces in the well-appointed kitchen featuring stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, and ample cabinet space, Crown Moldings: The timeless crown moldings add an elegant touch to the interior design, Electric Fireplace: Cozy up in front of the electric fireplace, creating a warm and inviting ambiance, Recessed Lighting: Energy-efficient and stylish recessed lighting brightens up your space, Master Shower with Dual Shower Heads: Experience luxury and comfort in the master bathroom, featuring a spacious shower with dual shower heads.Walk-In Closets in the Master Suite: The spacious walk-in closets provide ample storage space for all your clothing and accessories. Fenced Yard:  Enjoy privacy and security in your beautifully fenced yard, perfect for outdoor activities and relaxation. Port Saint Lucie is a vibrant and growing city that offers a high quality of life and numerous amenities. Located in St. Lucie County, you'll find easy access to beautiful beaches, parks, and waterways. Enjoy a wide variety of recreational activities, including golf, boating, and hiking. The city is known for its excellent schools, shopping centers, and dining options.
